    title Real-Time Routing Handler
  body
    header
      h1 Real-Time Routing Handler
      h2 Paths
      
      h3 bundle
      p A post to <code>/real_time_routing/bundle</code> with a JSON body containing <code>{"ids": #ARRAY#}</code> with an array of five integers will return <code>{"destination_campaign_id":#RANDOMLYSELECTEDINTEGER#}</code>.
      p Used to route a campaign by <code>destination_campaign_id</code>. 
      p Test the method with the following <code>curl</code> requests:
      pre curl -H "Content-Type: application/json" -XPOST -d '{"ids":[80,81,79,34,32]}' http://dry-castle-8995.herokuapp.com/real_time_routing/bundle.json
      pre curl -H "Content-Type: application/xml" -XPOST -d "<xml><ids>[80,81,79,34,32]</ids></xml>" http://localhost:9292/building/foo.xml
      pre curl -H "Content-Type: application/json" -XPOST -d '{"ids":[80,81,79,34,32]}' http://localhost:9292/building/foo.json
      pre curl -d http://localhost:9292/building/foo.html?city=city,num=calling_phone_number,press=keypress_4
      h3 bundificate
      p A post to <code>/real_time_routing/bundificate</code> with a JSON body containing <code>{"ids": #ARRAY#}</code> with an array of five integers will return <code>{"destination_campaign_id_from_network":#RANDOMLYSELECTEDINTEGER#}</code>.
      p Used to route a campaign by <code>destination_campaign_id_from_network</code>. 
      p Test the method with the following <code>curl</code> request:
      pre curl -H "Content-Type: application/json" -XPOST -d '{"ids":[82420,84321,7964,3424,632]}' http://dry-castle-8995.herokuapp.com/real_time_routing/bundificate
      
      h3 promo
      p A post to <code>/real_time_routing/direct</code> with an empty JSON body will return <code>{"destination_phone_number":#RANDOMLYSELECTEDPHONENUMBER#}</code>, with a randomly selected weather telephone number. 
      p Used to route a campaign by <code>destination_phone_number</code>. 
      p Test the method with the following <code>curl</code> request:
      pre curl -H "Content-Type: application/json" -XPOST -d '{}' http://dry-castle-8995.herokuapp.com/real_time_routing/promo

      h3 extensions
      p A post to <code>/real_time_routing/extensions</code> with an empty JSON body will return a number on the QA Invoca network in production that takes a keypress of 1. 
      p Used to route a campaign by <code>destination_phone_number</code>. 
      p Test the method with the following <code>curl</code> request:
      pre curl -H "Content-Type: application/json" -XPOST -d '{}' http://dry-castle-8995.herokuapp.com/real_time_routing/extensions
